Description: backport generic DMA mapping API compatibility
 Replace removed PCI DMA mapping aliases with centralized wrappers that use
 generic device DMA helpers when the legacy PCI alias family is unavailable.
Origin: backport, Linux generic DMA API compatibility adapted to NVIDIA 367.134
Forwarded: not-needed
Last-Update: 2026-07-20

